snippet.textDisplay:
God bless you Mohsin brother.... Very soulful... Excellent! I am not a Punjabi but I used subtitles to understand it, it is an enlightening song and I rate it similar to Bhajans, Prarthna, and Dua. I bow to the feeling behind writing this song.... I am grateful to you Mohsin brother for this composition... 
Lots of love and respect from India!!
